{"tid":88482,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"添好運老闆：做街舖好痛苦 好啲就加租","createTime":"2017-01-20T15:48:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-21T06:23:40.000Z","uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"85d990768123ec8529b0970183dd4ea50fa120f5","tid":88482,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T15:48:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170120&amp;guid=56200602&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170120%26guid%3D56200602%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant&d=b7DOn9OyI3Miq2JAdG7N8HvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=865ddeb9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170120%26guid%3D56200602%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant&h=0be5540c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170120&amp;guid=56200602&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n深水埗添好運點心專門店舖位業主準備標售，叫價達8,500萬元。添好運老闆麥桂培表示，深水埗總店的業主曾於月前詢問過，問他有沒有興趣購入舖位自用。「但我冇可能有咁大嚿錢吞得落，所以業主拎個舖去招標」。<br />\n<br />\n他指，做食肆一般租金佔總成本12%，目前18.5萬元一個月仍夠做，但舖位地點不是容易做，加租就有麻煩。由於銀行對個舖位的估價已逾8,000萬元，如果舖位賣得出，租金肯定要加，起碼加至逾20萬元。「仲有年半租約先到期，都係睇下點，加得誇張唔會留喺度」。<br />\n<br />\n麥桂培直言，「做街舖好痛苦，做好啲就一係被加租，一係就有人出高價搶你個位，做好少少就益咗人，已經三年冇喺街舖開新店」。他明言，如果做商場舖就相對穩陣、易計數，「至少唔會見你做好啲就諗加租」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcbtbryG6ngVNNVshhJuDwtkwSZd9Chaub8Hv1HAwJ64W?filename=fvv0z11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffvv0z11.jpg&h=49eb2e35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港只地產賺錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"268f8277e364b6e5048d06f97cac38eedca7d08a","tid":88482,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T15:51:08.000Z","msg":"差唔多成億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0f3a9637bb9e4c959d8